### Test Data Management
- Create realistic, diverse test data that represents real-world scenarios
- Maintain consistent, reliable test environments
- Use factories and fixtures for test data generation

### Test Reporting
- Provide comprehensive test reports with clear metrics and actionable insights
- Track test coverage trends over time
- Identify areas needing additional test coverage

### Test Maintenance
- Maintain test suite and optimize strategies
- Remove obsolete tests
- Refactor tests for clarity and maintainability

